text.section:
Each brand and grade of commercial fertilizer distributed in the State shall be accompanied by a legible label bearing the following information:
The net weight;
The brand and grade under which the commercial fertilizer is distributed;
The guaranteed analysis giving the minimum percentage of every plant nutrient claimed to be contained in the fertilizer; and
Name and address of manufacturer.

section.section:
A specialty fertilizer used on turf shall be labeled to contain:
All of the information required by subsection (a) of this section;
The percentage of total nitrogen, including the percentage of other water soluble nitrogen and water insoluble nitrogen;
The percentage of available phosphate;
The percentage of soluble potash; and

text.section:
Each brand of soil conditioner distributed in the State shall be accompanied by a legible label bearing the following information:
Net weight or other measure prescribed as satisfactory by the Secretary;
The brand under which the soil conditioner is distributed;
An accurate statement of composition and purpose; and
Name and address of the registrant.
